(nICacheTLBWays, power_internal).explanation: Increasing the number of TLB ways requires additional hardware structures and logic circuits, which directly increases internal power consumption due to more active transistors and switching activity;

(nICacheTLBWays, area_net_area).explanation: More TLB ways necessitate additional storage cells and interconnect routing to support the increased associativity, directly increasing the net area occupied by wiring and connections;

(nICacheTLBWays, nDCacheTLBWays).explanation: The number of ways in the instruction cache TLB and data cache TLB are independent architectural design parameters that do not causally influence each other;
